    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Merger Forms New Consultancy</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Eric Pfanner</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Pfanner, Eric</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>GlobalWorks.com and Liquid Digital Information Systems6</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GlobalWorks.com in New York and Liquid Digital Information Systems in New York, said yesterday that they had merged to form GlobalWorks in New York, a branding and communications consultancy. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
        <p>The combined agency will have 75 employees and revenue estimated at $10 million from clients like Lucent Technologies.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>GlobalWorks.com in New York and Liquid Digital Information Systems in New York, said yesterday that they had merged to form GlobalWorks in New York, a branding and communications consultancy. Terms were not disclosed.</p>
        <p>The combined agency will have 75 employees and revenue estimated at $10 million from clients like Lucent Technologies.</p>
        <p>Yuri Radzievsky, 54, president at GlobalWorks.com, becomes chairman and chief executive at GlobalWorks. Mans Angantyr, 34, president at Liquid Digital, becomes president and chief strategy officer.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
